name: Jessica White (@jesswhite@hachyderm.io)
summary:
I often tell people that it's better to rest and recover, than to push through, heal slower and/or do work you aren't proud of.

Practicing what I preach today. My body wins this round, but after a day's rest I reckon I'll be back to full form tomorrow.

Never feel guilty for not being well friends :blobfoxheartcute:
